data.description: Welcome to 1763 S del Norte Avenue!  This beautiful ranch-style, brick home sits on a quiet corner lot adjacent from a farm.  This property oozes peace and tranquility weather you are enjoying your morning coffee on the front patio overlooking the farm and lake or are grilling in the back yard, completely surrounded by lush vegetation. As you walk through the pergola to the front door you will immediately notice the pride of ownership all around.  Come inside and walk through the living room with abundant natural light through the large front window.  The large dining area sits just outside of the kitchen creating an open floor concept that is highly functional.   The primary bedroom lies on the main level and includes a tastefully updated bathroom, vibrant with color.  Walk downstairs into the large great room space which can be utilized for a living room, theater room, gym or a combination of the three.  The log-fired stove with full tile surround makes the basement an inviting space that can be enjoyed all winter long!  The back yard has so many possibilities that you will never want to leave.  Step down off of the large wooden deck onto the paver patio which is perfect for all of your outdoor furniture and a grill-masters dream!  The backyard includes a large garden and greenhouse which is perfect for growing whatever your heart desires.  This wonderful gem won't last long!
